{"tid":919681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南山邨命案】人妻背中刀喪命 57歲丈夫被捕","createTime":"2018-11-28T08:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T10:53:31.000Z","uid":157103,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"041e1b797934e62079129672f0f26f683361e6e4","tid":919681,"uid":157103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:34:38.000Z","msg":"【16:10】女事主送院後證實不治<br />\n石硤尾發生命案，下午3時許，警方接獲南山邨南樂樓一名57歲姓羅男子報案，指其40歲姓王妻子用刀自殺。現場消息稱，警員趕至現場時，發現女子背部插住一把刀，立即將其送院搶救，惟抵院後證實不治。警方經調查後，相信案件有可疑，將報案的丈夫拘捕，他被黑布蒙頭帶返警署調查。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181128&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58968510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181128%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58968510&d=FCE3QmlYR159ByaDNFjom%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=c5ff0b71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181128%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58968510&h=840ce56c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181128&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58968510</a><br />\nP.S.：有朋友住嗰度附近，話好似聽到有個男人係咁大大聲鬧落地獄，有冇朋友仔都喺附近住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779cf519e9d8c9fae355a5bcbc3a39a44dfa0e37","tid":919681,"uid":16471,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"自己插自己背脊都幾難"},{"pid":"6997768c8b33bd7f433d9fb31288fe1a8a9a5f5c","tid":919681,"uid":19712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"779cf519e9d8c9fae355a5bcbc3a39a44dfa0e37","tid":919681,"uid":16471,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"自己插自己背脊都幾難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"相當有可疑"},{"pid":"194cbaefd6fd3f746c12211140b0a7418c69f717","tid":919681,"uid":157103,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"一名57歲姓羅男子報案，指其40歲姓王<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: bl