al/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:12:03.000Z","msg":"明武宗朱厚照在位時，浙江錢塘發生命案，死者身中五刀，刀刀致命，錢塘縣令斷定此人系自殺身亡，在上報刑部後，刑部認為案理不通，駁回重審。事後，杭州府重審後仍以自殺身亡上報，刑部再次駁回並報送大理寺，此案遂上達天聽，進入皇帝的視野。<br />\n<br />\n朱厚照即正德皇帝，世人謂之荒唐暴戾，是少見的無道昏君，然此君了解案情後勃然大怒：「豈有身中五刀自斃者?欲將朕比晉惠乎?」於是嚴旨徹查杭州知府及錢塘縣令，最終查明兇手乃錢塘縣令妻侄也。<br />\n<br />\n一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9d74847700b2e7633c9c73e391e24d498b0d13","tid":919681,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"410ef4d5a1fa576fe0722a0d7dd3ae00b967037c","tid":919681,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f91fc12d3a235a96e89db23166b955ed9f207a0b","tid":919681,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d69dc53c10314c43196806ef61fe3c26fe27029","tid":919681,"uid":73613,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:05:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"廁所自殺就掩飾到"},{"pid":"32280a1019c332b8b16a8fb70714e168db6aa2d8","tid":919681,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"691ec44b6ff2ead091fd20f970e2b74b51df7983","tid":919681,"uid":32511,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"194cbaefd6fd3f746c12211140b0a7418c69f717","tid":919681,"uid":157103,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"一名57歲姓羅男子報案，指其40歲姓王<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">妻子用刀自殺